com.google.inject.tools.ideplugin
Interface JavaElement

public interface JavaElement

Representation of a Java element. Likely just a wrapper around IDE specific representations, for instance EclipseJavaElement is a wrapper around Eclipse's IJavaElement.

Author:
Darren Creutz (dcreutz@gmail.com)
